Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.46,0:02:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Once upon a time, in a faraway land...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.94,0:02:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There lived an honest man named Gosuke-don.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.02,0:02:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosuke-don was ever so slightly obtuse. {/dull}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But he was an honest hardworking man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.26,0:02:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosuke-don!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:02:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosuke-don's friend, Jaba-don,\N had just found himself a wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.13,0:02:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go home?{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.45,0:02:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.12,0:03:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure want meself a wife too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank ye very much for today's bread. {no clue wat he really means}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The sunset is the most beautiful today! So bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.57,0:03:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosuke! Gosuke! Gosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Headman. {庄屋}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The sunset is beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's bright red! Looks so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.91,0:03:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You cretin! It's bright red \Nbecause my storehouse is on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.00,0:03:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of loitering there, come quickly, Gosuke! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosuke! Save the heirloom that's been passed down in my family from inside that burning storehouse! {/bring/carry out}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be serious, Headman! \NGosuke will burn to death for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.44,0:03:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence! If this keeps up, \Nmy valuable heirloom will turn to ashes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.81,0:03:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A man as obtuse as Gosuke \Nwill definitely make it out alright! {now I'm thinking maybe they use nibui as "thick?"}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.76,0:04:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. Well, here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.06,0:04:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosuke! Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.07,0:04:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! That man is always so dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.41,0:04:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Now just come out with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I forgot... {assuming he means [to tell gosuke wha't s a heirloom]}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Heirloom, heirloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a heirloom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosuke-don had never heard this word before. {/what's a heirloom}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.42,0:04:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's burning down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Gosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's carrying something!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.99,0:04:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Gosuke! You've brought the hanging scroll, \Nwhich is my heirloom, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Headman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God! Gosuke, hurry up, show it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.71,0:04:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.03,0:04:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hair!{/mosquito}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Gloom!{/book}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Cretin, cretin, cretin, cretin, cretin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I was an idiot for asking you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! The storehouse! It's burned\Ndown completely! The damage is irreparable! {assumed heavy loss; great damage}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of this, this year's land tax will be twice the usual! {annual tribute; land tax}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.47,0:05:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't sustain that!{殺生}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosuke! It's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're playing dirty, Headman! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Headman, what do I do with this heirloom now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Do whatever with it, just get out of my sight! {お前にやるとっとともってけ from manga but unsure what he means}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.28,0:05:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.68,0:05:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Gosuke! Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot... Hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a rather obtuse man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to read, \Nso even if I have a book, I can't understand a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.80,0:06:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This looks like an interesting sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.52,0:06:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, if the land tax is doubled this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosuke-don was unable to think any further than that.{h}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, he thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.28,0:06:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Until he fell asleep on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a bit screwed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you, the Great Magician...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ria Kinakamo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! Pops. Pops, hello! {middle-aged man}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:06:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&HBAD3CC&\3c&H040C2D&\4c&H1224B4&\yshad5\fs50\bord1.5}Gramps!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Awake now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Let's start over, with passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you, the Great Magician... Ria Kinakamo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier, you summoned me \Nwith the "I'm a bit screwed" spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make your one wish come true. \NAsk for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so surprised, his eyes turned into dots. {to be stunned; to be surprised; one's eyes turn into dots (as in a cartoon)}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.29,0:07:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosuke wasn't surprised. \NHe simply had dotty eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I want a wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.26,0:07:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you mean a spouse? {dead pun, omekko = colloquial for "girl wife" and oyome-san in full, not diminuitive form}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:07:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Yahook up with me-kun should help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:08:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You use this arrow to pierce a woman's heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.24,0:08:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,to make that woman fall in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.10,0:08:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you marry her \Nwithout waiting another moment, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never shot an arrow before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, aren't you helpless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You draw a bow like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.38,0:08:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and aim it at the heart of the woman you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Release your right hand to let the arrow loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The hut of the woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And what if that woman \Ndoesn't live in a hut? {deadpun: do women keep pigeons (hato)?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're really not making it easy for me! {lit: I have to take care of you}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The heart is the organ inside you. {/heart is what heart is called}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's located in the chest, around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You aim to here, like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:08:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.52,0:08:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My chest suddenly feels so dense. {/tight}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this pleasant warmth \Nspreading through my chest? {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,From just looking at this man's face,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,my heart is pounding...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.22,0:09:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.12,0:09:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This well-proportioned square head... {/neat}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The round and cute eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The more you look at it, \Nthe more appealing his big face becomes. {/interesting}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.84,0:09:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,His slowly moving mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.03,0:09:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,His peaceful and carefree composure...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.35,0:09:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! How come I never noticed \Nthat a man so wonderful was right here...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.12,0:09:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Jaba-don!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Please meet my wife too. {/look at}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Ria. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.47,0:10:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What a beauty! {beautiful woman; pretty girl​}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd you do it, Gosuke?\NI can't take my eyes off her! {こげなどすごいおなご not sure what he means}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.89,0:10:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,E-he.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.81,0:10:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me that "E-he"!{/I don't understand ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How could a man like you find himself \Na wife {\i1}that{\i0\fsp3} {\fsp0}gorgeous! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hurt my Gosuke-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't deserve to be any closer \Nthan several miles from him! {lit: someone like you should fly to the other side of the mountain, I suspect some proverb but too lazy}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My Dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.61,0:10:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Jaba-don!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.30,0:10:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ria, save Jaba-don.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But he was bothering you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Jaba-don is a dear friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.29,0:10:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ria...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.46,0:10:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What a forgiving man...{/kind}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants me to save Jaba-don, \Nwho just strangled him mere moments ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.22,0:10:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosuke-san... No, Gosuke-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I just fell in love with you once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:10:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Jaba-don!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.55,0:11:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, my Okio-chan! {g, not in manga}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H181E6D&}Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry, Jaba-don.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.12,0:11:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive us for this misstep. {lit: for being this way}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Jaba-don-san, forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.69,0:11:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart was so selfish before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But with his warmth,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,bit by bit, he made me open up to the world. {to relax; to soften; to relieve (e.g. stress, tension); to remove (e.g. doubt)}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.91,0:11:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosuke-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I am happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I offer my gratitude to the heavens, {/thank god}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.29,0:11:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,for the chance to live with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Gosuke-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?! \NGosuke found himself a beautiful wife?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.07,0:12:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Precisely so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, that's some steaming nonsense! \NAnyone but Gosuke...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.41,0:12:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.07,0:12:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Gosuke-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I tell you, Headman?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:13:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That damned Gosuke, finding himself \Na dazzling lady... Unacceptable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.99,0:13:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Gosuke! {g, yai in manga}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Headman!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Honored to meet you, Headman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Ria, the wife of Gosuke-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I must greet them appropriately, \Nlest I bring shame upon Gosuke-sama. {/embarrassing thoughts - unsure if it's gosuke who'll be thinking bad or he'll be thought bad about}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So bouncy... {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.62,0:13:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So pretty! Gosuke receiving her as a wife \Nis a terrible waste! Impossible beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosuke, remember how you failed to carry my heirloom \Nout of my burning storehouse the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.35,0:13:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,As a punishment, your land tax is 30 times the usual this year! And you're to bring it to me by tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,30 times the usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cause you've never seen so much in your life! \NIt'll be 180 bushels of rice by tomorrow! {それだけたくさんということじゃ - unsure what he means}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you can gather that much!{hope}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,However, being compassionate as I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,in lieu of rice bushels, \NI'll accept your wife as payment! {lit: instead of land tax, give me your wife}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.08,0:14:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll forgive your land tax fully! {/excuse you}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.55,0:14:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.63,0:14:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, you're annoying! \NHave you ever tried to think before talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.91,0:14:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking advantage of Gosuke-sama's good nature...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ria...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.39,0:14:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosuke-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.49,0:14:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me that look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.40,0:14:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It can sadden even me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, I shouldn't lose my temper, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't fight others.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I must pacify my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You pest! Gosuke, are you\Ngiving your wife any discipline at all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:15:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"First of all, apologize calmly," right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Headman-chan. {床 - not sure if that counts for other word or not}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Headman-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.93,0:15:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It was because Headman-chan yanked\Nmy hand so suddenly, that my hand accidentally slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But dear, I'm not going to become yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.76,0:15:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, because it's clear as a day that Gosuke-sama \Nwill collect 180 bushels, 30 times his land tax by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.67,0:15:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you not right in the head?! {/idiot}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.88,0:15:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way in hell \Nsomeone as clumsy as him can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And what'll you do if he does?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.38,0:15:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosuke-sama's so humble that\Nhe doesn't stand out particularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But really, he's a wonderful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He's nothing like you, who let the village headmanship go to his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Are you saying that if it wasn't for the headmanship, I'd be inferior to Gosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly why \NI'm so enchanted by Gosuke-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.30,0:16:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.78,0:16:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Supposing Gosuke is as great as you say \Nand he manages to collect 180 bushels by tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.99,0:16:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let that dunce replace me as the village headman! {h}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.84,0:16:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much \Nfor making Gosuke-sama the next village headman. {/letting become}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,However! If he fails to collect it, \Nyou'll be mine, you hear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that clear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the witnesses, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.49,0:16:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.64,0:16:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please remember \Nwhat you just heard, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What can they ever pull off with just one person?{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This unearthly beauty is already mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosuke, have you really made such a reckless promise,\Neven though the rice has already been harvested?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight will be the last night \Nyou two will spend together, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.45,0:16:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You poor fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight is our last night... {/we part}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:16:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.66,0:16:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ria, be happy... {https://ja.hinative.com/questions/18564313}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying now? \NThat's so depressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, why don't we do some work?{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we going to do so late at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The light of compassion that nurtures life,\Nplease bestow a piece of the sun's blessing upon us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ria!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! I'm counting on you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.79,0:17:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Raincloud Taro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.85,0:17:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.64,0:17:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.98,0:17:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You... Can...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Your... Best... {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's still not nearly enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just use the Growth Spray \NExponential Growth Formula. {増殖スプレー 倍々増殖ん}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Double!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.99,0:18:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Double!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! It's just like magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.19,0:18:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm a magician, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.11,0:18:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the first thing I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.34,0:18:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:19:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just seeing some dream... \NA nightmare right now! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.39,0:19:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's real rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Headman, you gotta keep your promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Rice? Rice... {tlc, g, could be "rice" but idk what he means}{19:10: I' hearing "こめや、こめ"\NI think he might just be repeating "米/rice" over and over again due to shock.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all witnesses, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.93,0:19:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll you do?{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be... This can't... Ah, rice... {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, Gosuke-don, now the village headman, \Nlived happily ever after with Ria.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you'd think,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.08,0:19:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but Ria's magic only lasts ten days.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I fell in love with this man \Nbecause of Yahook up with me-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.64,0:19:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've got bad news for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I can't marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,As promised, I made your one wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.03,0:19:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But with this, my work here is done. {/role completed}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.64,0:20:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta return to the Magic Realm soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.94,0:20:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.86,0:20:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosuke-don couldn't understand what was going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.25,0:20:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,As usual, his eyes were like two dots.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.54,0:20:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.88,0:20:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The magic of love had been dispelled...{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.36,0:20:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, I can't stop crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.60,0:20:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ria...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.54,0:20:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I have to return home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:43.89,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H468118&}Turn back the clock to return to the place where we met {時を戻して出逢いの場所であなたと も一度}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.74,0:20:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I return to the Magic Realm, \NI will completely disappear from your memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.89,0:20:50.48,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H468118&}So we could start over once again {はじめからやりなおして}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.94,0:20:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I know for a fact that you can find yourself a wonderful wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:54.37,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H468118&}That's what I want... {みたいのに･･････}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be praying for that too.{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.00,0:21:02.92,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H468118&}Your eyes... {あなたの瞳 }
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosuke-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.91,0:21:07.22,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H468118&}Because I need to forget them, {忘れる為に}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.10,0:21:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Good day, nice to meet you-yu-yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:15.25,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H468118&}Even though I was the one who said goodbye... {私から言う「さよなら」 なのに}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:19.38,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H468118&}From the bottom of my heart, {心のすみで}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ria...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.41,0:21:23.22,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H468118&}I'm screaming in pain {叫んでいるの}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.49,0:21:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, Gosuke had apparently married \Na beautiful and kind woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.67,0:21:31.33,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H468118&}I don't want to leave the warmth in my heart {離れたくない 胸のぬくもり}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.87,0:21:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.06,0:21:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Village headman, I beg you! \NPlease subsidize my land tax this year!{/make smaller}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.83,0:21:35.92,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H468118&}I see you in the city... {街の中であなたは - dont hear the anata part but gotta be somewhere here}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.37,0:21:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.47,0:21:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:40.40,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H468118&}I see myself in the rain... {雨の中で私は}
Comment: 0,0:21:38.63,0:21:40.42,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H291881&\an1}See myself, myself {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Subsequently, Gosuke's personality \Nwon him the trust of the villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:48.84,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H468118&}Eventually, I'm cooling down in time {時の中で冷めていく}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And as the Great Headman, \Nhe lived with the villagers happily ever after.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.85,0:21:58.13,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H468118&}Turn back the clock to return to the place where we met {時を戻して出逢いの場所であなたと も一度}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.13,0:22:04.72,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H468118&}So we could start from the beginning over once again {はじめからやりなおして}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.48,0:22:08.89,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H468118&}That's what I want... {みたいのに･･････}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.85,0:22:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru! My Cook-san is amazing! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.92,0:22:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.51,0:22:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,With that cute Cook-san on our side, \Nwe've nothing to fear from Harako's cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.01,0:22:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Take one straight stick... {棒が一本あったとさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.77,0:22:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a leaf? {はっぱかな}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.27,0:22:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a leaf...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.28,0:22:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a frog now! {はっぱじゃないよ　かえるだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.34,0:23:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Magical Taruruuto-kun:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.86,0:23:01.82,Sign,,0,0,0,,Episode 75 \NTaruru! Cook-san {たるる!コックさん}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.03,0:23:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Taruru! Cook-san. {たるる!コックさん}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.83,0:23:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So delicious! {g}
